            "title": "彭博 : 發改委限制內房採用「1+N」境外貸款",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">《彭博》引述知情人士報道，內地當局正限制企業使用「1+N」的常見境外貸款架構，尤其是對內房企業。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">報道稱，國家發展和改革委員會已告知銀行人士，將不再允許企業以此架構進行跨境借款。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">這類貸款期限通常只有364天，可延期，客觀效果是令借款人未經發改委同意，就訂定貸款協議，這類貸款有助企業資金到位延遲問題，由於當局收緊期限超過一年的境外貸款審批，資金到位延遲的情況日益普遍。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">發改委目的在促使企業和銀行在債務再融資前加強風險管理，同時也加強了對境外借款的審查，包括要求借款人提供有關還款計劃的更多細節。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16422333-%e5%bd%ad%e5%8d%9a-%e7%99%bc%e6%94%b9%e5%a7%94%e9%99%90%e5%88%b6%e5%85%a7%e6%88%bf%e6%8e%a1%e7%94%a8%e3%80%8c1n%e3%80%8d%e5%a2%83%e5%a4%96%e8%b2%b8%e6%ac%be",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230901_FI_China-Property_source_web_-shutterstock_1200.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-23 17:43:42",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "大埔逸瓏灣3房1,030萬元成交     3年蝕9%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=16400427&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中原地產新界東豪宅白石角分行促成成交，大埔白石角逸瓏灣最新錄高座20座低層C室，單位實用面積907平方呎，3房連套房間隔，開價約1,100萬元，日前議價後以1,030萬元沽出，實用面積呎價約11,356元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新買家為同區租客，近日決定轉租為買，原業主於2023年以1,135萬元購入上址，持貨約3年，現轉手賬面蝕105萬元離場，單位期內貶值9.3%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16400427-%e5%a4%a7%e5%9f%94%e9%80%b8%e7%93%8f%e7%81%a33%e6%88%bf1030%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4-3%e5%b9%b4%e8%9d%959",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-23 17:19:25",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "德福花園2房戶528.8萬成交  業主04年買入 物業升值近2.2倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=16400338&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">利嘉閣地產新啟德-現崇山分行促成九龍灣德福花園H座高層5室的二手成交個案，單位實用面積約517方呎，為2房間隔，望樓景。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新買家為區內客，主原叫價615萬元，經多番議價後，終以528.8萬元成交，折合實用面積呎價約10,228元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">據悉，業主於2004年以約166萬元購入，持貨至今易手，現帳面大幅獲利逾362萬元，期內物業升值近2.2倍。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">屋苑同類型單位目前約有11個放盤，最低入場費由約460萬元起。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16400338-%e5%be%b7%e7%a6%8f%e8%8a%b1%e5%9c%922%e6%88%bf%e6%88%b6528-8%e8%90%ac%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4-%e6%a5%ad%e4%b8%bb04%e5%b9%b4%e8%b2%b7%e5%85%a5-%e7%89%a9%e6%a5%ad%e5%8d%87%e5%80%bc%e8%bf%912-2%e5%80%8d",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-23 17:19:25",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "本港二手樓價按周微跌0.13%　連跌兩周",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=16384753&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">反映本港二手住宅樓價走勢的中原城市領先指數（CCL）最新報159.34，按周微跌0.13%，連跌兩星期，為逾一年以來首次出現連跌，兩周累計跌幅接近0.9%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">按物業類型劃分，大型單位樓價表現較弱，按周跌近0.9%，連跌兩周累計跌幅達1.38%；中小型單位樓價則輕微回升。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">分區方面，九龍區樓價跌幅最為顯著，按周跌近1.5%，創今年1月中旬以來的最大單周跌幅。新界西則表現強勢，按周升近2%，為1月底以來最大升幅。新界東及港島區樓價則大致靠穩。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中原地產分析指出，隨着近日恒生指數回升，世界盃賽事即將結束，加上多個新盤陸續開售，樓市交投有望恢復活躍。該行相信，短期樓價上升方向未變，但升幅將會減慢。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16384753-%e6%9c%ac%e6%b8%af%e4%ba%8c%e6%89%8b%e6%a8%93%e5%83%b9%e6%8c%89%e5%91%a8%e5%be%ae%e8%b7%8c0-13%e3%80%80%e9%80%a3%e8%b7%8c%e5%85%a9%e5%91%a8",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_PROPERTY_INDEX_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-23 17:19:25",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "商務部：上半年實際使用外資金額按年降5% 單計6月則升15.1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">商務部最新數據顯示，今年上半年全國實際使用外資(FDI)金額達4,021.4億元(人民幣．下同)，按年降5%；單計6月份則錄得按年增長15.1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240415_FI_source-ap_ChinaEco-6.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240415_FI_source-ap_ChinaEco-6.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上半年全國新設立外商投資企業3.16萬家，較去年同期增加5.3%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">商務部外國投資管理司司長孟華婷表示，上半年FDI按年跌幅，已較去年同期收窄10.2個百分點；其中5月及6月均實現按年正增長，反映吸收外資正呈現回穩向好趨勢。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">她進一步指出，當局將進一步塑造吸引外資新優勢，做好擴增量、穩存量、提質量各項工作，並會穩妥有序深化增值電信、生物技術、外商獨資醫院及職業技能培訓機構等領域的開放試點，同時加快修訂出台關於外國投資者併購境內企業的相關規定。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16422315-%e5%95%86%e5%8b%99%e9%83%a8%ef%bc%9a%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e5%af%a6%e9%9a%9b%e4%bd%bf%e7%94%a8%e5%a4%96%e8%b3%87%e9%87%91%e9%a1%8d%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e9%99%8d5-%e5%96%ae%e8%a8%886%e6%9c%88",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/04/20250403_FI_source-ap_MOFCOM-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-23 17:19:23",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "全日收市｜港股收升318點  金融股揚升  內需股受壓",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股全日升318點，金融股午後上揚，中國財政部長藍佛安政治局會議前夕撰文，稱將推有力措施釋放消費及投資活力。國際金融股也向好，滙控(00005)成升市主力，鋁業股全日領升，消費股捱沽。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"內地銀行。AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250424_FI_source-ap_China_Banks.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"內地銀行。AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250424_FI_source-ap_China_Banks.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">內地銀行。AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數全日報25,210，升318點或1.28%，今早開市報24,966點，升73點或0.3%，最低見24,876，跌16點或0.06%，隨即節節向上，全日最高見25,267，升375點或1.5%，為上午高位。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"內地銀行。AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250424_FI_source-ap_China_Banks.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"內地銀行。AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250424_FI_source-ap_China_Banks.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">內地銀行。AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250305_FI_source-web_HSBC-5.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250305_FI_source-web_HSBC-5.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：滙控官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國鋁業2023年度年報\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240425_FI_source-web_02600-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國鋁業2023年度年報\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240425_FI_source-web_02600-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中國鋁業2023年度年報</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：農夫山泉官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230719_FI_source-web_09633-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：農夫山泉官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230719_FI_source-web_09633-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：農夫山泉官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"內地銀行。AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250424_FI_source-ap_China_Banks.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">內地銀行。AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250305_FI_source-web_HSBC-5.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：滙控官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國鋁業2023年度年報\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240425_FI_source-web_02600-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中國鋁業2023年度年報</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：農夫山泉官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230719_FI_source-web_09633-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：農夫山泉官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數全日報4,698，升30點或0.65%，今日開報4,677點，升9點或0.2%；</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生國企指數全日報8,352，升101點或1.23%，今日以8,266點開市，升15點或0.19%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">大市成交2,334.8億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月期指全日報25,210，升294點或1.18%，低水1點 ; 科指半日報4,700，升22點或0.47%，高水2點 ; 國指半日報8.350，升94點或1.14%，低水3點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)破頂，見162元，升1.95%，貢獻恒指36點，成升市功臣，據報與恒生整合7個職能部門包括企業傳訊部、公司秘書及企業管治部、風險監控及合規部、資訊科技部、內部審計部，財務部，以及營運總監。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250305_FI_source-web_HSBC-5.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250305_FI_source-web_HSBC-5.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">金融股午後升幅擴大，建設銀行(00939)升2.22%，報8.74元 ; 工商銀行(01398)升2.43%，報7.17元 ; 中國銀行(03988)升2.31%，報5.31元 ; 中國人壽(02628)升2.88%，報28.6元，合共貢獻恒指70點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">友邦保險(01299)升2.21%，報78.6元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">兩大鋁業股領漲，中國鋁業(02600)升6.28%，報8.63元，為表現最佳藍籌股 ; 中國宏橋(01378)升3.37%，報23.94元，美伊戰事持續，倫敦期鋁價升。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國鋁業2023年度年報\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240425_FI_source-web_02600-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國鋁業2023年度年報\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240425_FI_source-web_02600-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國鋁業2023年度年報</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美團(03690)午後升，收升4.36%，報87.3元，貢獻恒指31點 ; 騰訊(00700)收升1.04%，報445.2，該股昨天急跌7%，昨天數據顯示，騰訊成為公募基金二季度減持市值最多的個股，北水連續四日淨沽騰訊，今日反彈。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：農夫山泉官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230719_FI_source-web_09633-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：農夫山泉官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230719_FI_source-web_09633-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：農夫山泉官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內需股跌，農夫山泉(09633)挫5.73%，報40.44元，為表現最差藍籌股 ; 鳴鳴很忙(01768)收跌7.55%，報355.2元，IPO基石投資者將於下周二（28日）解禁，涉及642.36萬股，約佔已發行股官權2.98% ; 百威亞太(06160)跌1.37%，報193.8元 ; 老鋪黃金(06181)跌1.31%，報392元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">晶片股壓抑大市，中芯(00981)跌2.95%，報70.75元，影響恒指13點 ; 華虹宏力(01347)跌7.49%，報149.4元。</p>\n</div>",
