            "title": "在岸人民幣兌美元收升34點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">在岸人民幣兌美元官方收報6.7706，較上日上漲34點。</p>\n</div>",
